                        "content": "A hospitalized client has a prescription for dextroamphetamine daily. The unit nurse collaborates with the dietitian to limit the amount of which item on the client's dietary trays?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nDextroamphetamine is a central nervous system (CNS) stimulant. Caffeine is a stimulant also, so caffeine intake needs to be limited in the client taking this medication. The client needs to be taught to limit caffeine intake as well. It is not necessary to limit fat, starch, or protein while taking this medication.",
                        "id": "26c12a772cb640a78ad49d3ea5ff98b7",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "fc66d7f001d4457f9a3eedda011d8312",
                                "content": "2 hours before bedtime"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "9c0a05b9315446adbd6508f07dbdbb0a",
                                "content": "After supper each night"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "91a95dba4e5344a78ab40fbc6431957f",
                                "content": "Just before going to sleep"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "aba3b82c4aaa457eb4929931744b696d",
                                "content": "At least 6 hours before bedtime"
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
